25:43.299 --> 25:44.972
Jordan never spoke in class.

25:44.997 --> 25:46.530
After a couple of weeks,

25:46.532 --> 25:48.632
I asked him why, and...

25:48.634 --> 25:51.618
he said that he had been speaking to me.

25:51.620 --> 25:53.470
Through the art that he was making.

25:53.472 --> 25:55.322
The more Wendy sells this romance,

25:55.324 --> 25:57.491
the more this jury's gonna
feel betrayed when they find out

25:57.493 --> 25:59.426
Jordan was underage.

25:59.428 --> 26:01.561
- It's a thing of beauty.
- Well, Edward's mirror

26:01.563 --> 26:03.530
