26:27.473 --> 26:30.140
And it became clear
how he felt about me.

26:30.142 --> 26:32.909
Wendy's brought a
little show-and-tell.

26:32.911 --> 26:34.578
So, a student with a crush.

26:34.580 --> 26:36.079
Sounds kind of dicey.

26:36.081 --> 26:37.280
Why not transfer him

26:37.282 --> 26:39.057
to a new class?

26:39.082 --> 26:41.084
I did not want to turn my back

26:41.086 --> 26:42.219
on Jordan.

26:42.221 --> 26:44.087
Like his parents had.

26:44.089 --> 26:48.625
But pretty soon I realized
that I was lying to myself

26:48.627 --> 26:51.395
and that I loved Jordan.

26:51.397 --> 26:55.032
After that, it was
just a matter of time,

26:55.034 --> 26:57.234
waiting till after he turned 17

26:57.236 --> 26:58.835
to express that love.

26:58.837 --> 27:01.204
Heart rates up, eye focus softening.

27:01.206 --> 27:03.740
The jury ate her testimony up.

27:03.742 --> 27:05.459
Right where we want 'em.

27:05.461 --> 27:08.028
- I love a surprise party.
