27:28.617 --> 27:30.016
when he was 16 years old

27:30.018 --> 27:32.819
and you are guilty of statutory rape?

27:32.821 --> 27:35.489
Susan needs to
be kept far from boys.

27:35.491 --> 27:37.924
And my husband.

27:37.926 --> 27:41.027
